dict.string: Exhale, spread your fingers wide, and fold forward, hinging at the hips.
Inhale, ground your hands, and look halfway up with a flat back.
Exhale, float to the back of your mat, and lower halfway down with elbows grazing your side.
Inhale, roll on the tops of your feet, open the chest, and straighten your arms, upward facing dog.
Exhale, tuck your toes, push back, and lift your hips with straight arms, downward facing dog.
Lower your left foot to the mat at a 45 degree angle, and bring your right foot foward between your hands. Inhale, lift your arms up, and lift up to warrior one.
On an exhale, pivot to the back of your mat for warrior one on the left side.
Inhale, and windmill out to warrior 2, arms parallel to the ground and gaze over your left hand.
On an exhale, turn to the front of the mat for warrior two on the right side.
On an exhale, plant your hands down by your right foot and float to the back of the mat, lowering halfway down to chaturanga.
Inhale, roll on the tops of your feet, open the chest, and straighten your arms, upward facing dog.
Exhale, tuck your toes, push back, and lift your hips with straight arms, downward facing dog.
Inhale, look forward, bring your feet between your hands, and straighten your spine.
Exhale, and fold your chest toward your legs.
Inhale, and lift your head again, keeping a flat back.
Exhale, and come all the way up to standing.
